            @*Project description*@
            <font face="arial" color="#ffffff" style="font-size:20px; bottom:-650px; position:absolute; left: 10px; text-align:start;  width:1000px;">
                &emsp;Just Jump! is a simple 3D mobile game with low poly graphics, from the category of arcade games. In this game you have to jump with a cube on different platforms until the end of the level.
                The game has over 75 levels and many skins for your cube. The levels are short and simple, some of them being special. With the pennies and precious stones collected you can buy chests and skins for your cube.
                The game consumes few resources (works on weak phones) and takes up little storage space.

                <br>
                &emsp;The game is free, official, and can be downloaded from the Play Store:
                <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Lybra.JustJump" target="_blank" style="color:white; text-decoration:none"><b>JustJump! - PlayStore</b></a>
                <br>

                <ul style="list-style-type:circle">
                    <li>Version: 2.2</li>
                    <li>Age: PEGI 3</li>
                    <li>Category: Arcade</li>
                    <li>Reviews: 4,9/5,0</li>
                    <li>Downloads: 448</li>
                    <li>Android version: 4.4 - the newest</li>
                    <li>Size: 39MB</li>
                    <li>Last update: 15.5.2020 </li>
                    <li>Release date: 21.12.2018 (version: 1.0)</li>
                    <li>Project status: ended (there will be no more updates)</li>
                    <li>Game status: released,official</li>
                </ul>
            </font>

