                In this game you are on a territory between four huge walls. This territory is guarded by enemies whose purpose is to kill you.
                For this reason you have to get different resources and weapons to survive. Your goal in this game is to escape outside the walls.
                The game is survival and shooter and does not require internet connection (it is singleplayer, offline).
                It takes up little storage space and is well optimized.

                <br>
                &emsp;The game is free, unofficial (beta), and can be downloaded from the Play Store:
