                &emsp;EndlessFire is an indie 3D First-Person Shooter game/FPS game(semi-survival,lowpoly and offline/singleplayer),created by one person with UnityEngine.
                In this game you are a soldier who has to do different special missions.
                You will complete these missions with the help of items and weapons that you will find on the map.
                During the missions you will encounter enemies who want to kill you. For this reason you will have to defend yourself with the weapons you will find in the game.
                The missions will take place on a territory full of enemy military bases.
                The game has a simple, low poly, "flat" graphics, consumes few resources (500MB VRAM and 300 MB RAM), takes up little storage space, is well optimized and runs on old systems.
                <br>
                &emsp;The game is free, unofficial (alpha), and can be downloaded from the Itch.io:
